_pdbx_database_remark.text   
;HETEROGEN
NOTE THAT IN THE CRYSTAL A REACEMIC MIXTURE OF THE LIGAND
C1B WAS USED. THE PHENOLATE OXYGEN MAKES SHORT HYDROGEN
BONDS WITH THE HYDROXYL GROUP OF SER195 AND A WATER.
;
